      <acqinfo id="aspace_0797d47f18231655d17ca43b5ef26df0">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The volume of minutes was the gift of the Yale Cooperative Corporation, 1902. The ledger was purchased in 1978.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_e61ed0ca01bf06b2bddb31010589d051">
