      <dsc>
         <c id="ref10" level="series">
            <did>
               <unittitle>Inventory</unittitle>
            </did>
            <scopecontent id="aspace_da6e32842c78f86923811ee42a7739d0">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The papers of the Yale Cooperative Corporation consist of two bound volumes and a few loose items removed from the volumes. The first volume is a manuscript notebook containing minutes of the Yale Cooperative Society between 1885 and 1891, its constitution, and a few clippings and minor publications of the Society. The other volume is a ledger of the Yale Cooperative Corporation, kept for the years 1896 through 1898, and 1903 through 1905.</p>
            </scopecontent>
